msgctxt "56_Motoyama"
msgid "*cough* *wheeze*"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68_Saejima"
msgid "You know, I lost everythin' 25 years ago myself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80_Motoyama"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92_Saejima"
msgid ""
"I'm not askin' ya to believe me, but that's why I came back. To find out "
"the truth."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104_Motoyama"
msgid "So, what really happened back then... and why?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116_Saejima"
msgid "Still tryin' to piece that together. But I can tell ya this much..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128_Saejima"
msgid ""
"That's a question ya don't wanna ask. It'll land you in deeper shit than "
"this, and I couldn't bear to see that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140_Saejima"
msgid "I'm sorry, Aniki. One thing's for sure, though..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "152_Motoyama"
msgid "Yeah?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "164_Saejima"
msgid "Sasai-san is alive."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "176_Motoyama"
msgid "Really? After all this time...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "248_Saejima"
msgid "He's changed a lot, and not for the better. But he's still our boss."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "260_Motoyama"
msgid "So he's alive... maybe that's enough."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "272_Saejima"
msgid "What're ya gonna do next?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "284_Motoyama"
msgid ""
"I'm gonna leave. Somehow, I feel like I can finally shut the door on the "
"demons that've haunted me all these years."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "296_Saejima"
msgid "Yeah?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "308_Motoyama"
msgid ""
"And I'm sorry. Truth is, you were only a kid in way over your head. Just "
"like I was."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "320_Saejima"
msgid "Don't worry 'bout it. Just take care of yourself, Aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "332_Motoyama"
msgid "I will."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "344_Saejima"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "356_Motoyama"
msgid "But tell me something, Saejima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "368_Saejima"
msgid "Yes, sir?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "380_Motoyama"
msgid ""
"Kamurocho's been my prison for half my life. I've been too scared to set "
"foot outside this city."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "392_Saejima"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "404_Motoyama"
msgid ""
"I lost my boss, my rank in the Tojo... but I didn't have the courage to "
"skip town and live my own life."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "416_Saejima"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "428_Motoyama"
msgid ""
"But you broke out of prison, didn't you? What did it feel like, breathing "
"free for the first time in a quarter century?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "440_Saejima"
msgid ""
"Frankly, I still ain't used to it. I'm like a ghost payin' a visit from the "
"past."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "452_Motoyama"
msgid "Oh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "464_Saejima"
msgid "Still, it's not all bad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "476_Motoyama"
msgid "No?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "500_Saejima"
msgid ""
"I made some new friends. Might be on the run, but I ain't lonely no more. "
"And that's good enough."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "512_Motoyama"
msgid "Saejima..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "524_Saejima"
msgid "People are what make people happy. You're not in this alone, Aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "536_Saejima"
msgid ""
"If things get rough out there, don't lose it. Just come on back to "
"Kamurocho. Back to your family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "548_Motoyama"
msgid "I'll remember that. Thanks, Saejima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "560_Saejima"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "620_Saejima"
msgid "(25 years of hell, huh? Motoyama-aniki had it rough, too.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "632_Saejima"
msgid ""
"(Welp, I got things to do. First, better tell Tadokoro how the gig went. I "
"reckon he'll send his stooge to the hideout.)"
msgstr ""